<p>Remarks:</p>
<ul class="list">
<li>On the first day, the LGM will open at 8:30 (pick up the badge, registration for the supper, ...)</li>
<li>Talks will be scheduled each day from 9:00 to 11:15 and from 14:50 to 17:40.</li>
<li>Each session will last 30 minutes, with 5 minutes recovery time inbetween.</li>
<li>There will be a lightning talks session each day from 14:15 to 14.45</li>
<li>The Great LGM Supper will be on friday night and will cost CAD $ 30 (wine or beer included)</li>
<li>Those who miss the program draft can find it <a href="skin/program_080906.jpg">here</a>
</ul>
<p>The list of the talks is a tiny part of what will happen at the Libre Graphics Meeting: you can have a look at the <a href="participant.php.html">list of participants</a> which have allowed us to show their name, you may find people you might want to talk to!</p>
